  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Modifies Attack, Multiattack, Charge, Reckless strike and Exploit weakness. <br />On hit, triggers a Strength vs Test against target's Strength/Endurance.</p><hr /><p>On attacker's success, the target becomes Rooted <br />The target must spend 1 action to repeat the vs Test to escape.<br />Impale must be maintained; it ends if the attacker moves, attacks or defends. <br />Cannot be used through an occupied hex. Cannot be combined with Stunning blow or Trip. <br /><br />While maintaining Impale you may use 1 action to repeat the vs Test to push the target 1 hex sideways. <br />You may also move together with the target 1 hex forward or sideways. <br /></p>",
